In a skillet, over medium-high heat, add oil and ground beef and fry, stirring occasionally until browned. Stir in onions and green bell pepper, and continue to fry another 2 to 3 minutes until lightly brown. Stir in pinto beans, UNCLE BEN'S(R) Flavor Infusions Spanish Style Rice, and water. Keep stirring to combine. Bring to boil, then reduce to medium heat and simmer covered for 15 minutes or until water is absorbed. Garnish with fresh cilantro.